label: Maintenance Procedures - Conditional Maintenance Task Ontology
abstract: The OMPD Conditional Mainteance Task Ontology captures conditial task information (i.e. in response to some limit or functional failure) present in some industrial maintenance procedures.
contributors: Tim French: The University of Western Australia,Caitlin Woods: The University of Western Australia and Equonto,Melinda Hodkiewicz: The University of Western Australia
creator: The University of Western Australia & Equonto Pty. Ltd.
title: Ontology for Maintenance Procedure Documentation (OMPD) Conditional Maintenance Task Ontology
